    exhibit:"<span class='cy'>CHANGE REQUEST CR-114</span>\n  Requestor: Marketing lead (stakeholder)\n  Description: Add a new reporting dashboard not in the baseline\n  Submitted: informally via email, no impact analysis yet\n  Production impact: none yet; affects scope + schedule\n\n<span class='dim'>Types: Standard | Normal | Emergency</span>",
